<br>
Sun Reavers cast Fear that seems to land about 1 time in 100 for a fraction of a second.<br>
<br>
Both proc a disease based curse so Earth pet is good as it is immune.<br>
<br>
Occasionally you see some named Sun Revenants spawn that can drop some decent items. The names are a couple of levels higher with slightly more HP's.<br>
